1c) i: some of the predictors seem to be related to the response. ii: spesifically year, origin displacement and weight iii: the coeficient for year sugests that every year cars get 0.777 higher mpg.

1d) the fitted vs residuals shows a clear pattern tending towards the lower right. This sugests we do not have a true linear dependency in our model. QQ plot looks good. obs 14 seems to have a high leverage.
